title: Iowa Legislative Services Bureau, House of Representatives District Boundaries, Iowa, 2002
name: Iowa Legislative Services Bureau, House of Representatives District Boundaries, Iowa, 2002
description:
Abstract:
    This coverage contains polygons representing the Iowa House of Representatives district boundaries. These boundaries were created by redistricting after the 2000 census. The original data was provided in shapefile format by the Iowa Legislative Services Bureau. 
Purpose:
    This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources.

author.source: Legislative Services Bureau; Casey J Kohrt
